text: Can't believe the new parents on our team didn't pick a weather-related name for their children. :baby:

Regarding previous years questions, because they allowed us to buy previous years questions I'm wondering if that is going to be a question or maybe even an hour of questions in this year's trivia. For example they could take the first letter of different questions and different hours to spell a phrase. I'll be bringing some of my previous years questions. Along with Stacia we should have a pretty good set.
Is it wrong that I'm annoyed it's going to be 50 degrees here next weekend? Trivia Weekend should be cold and snowy, not springlike!
